FBIS3-17312 "drsov058_g_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-058 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Mar 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus World Bank To Grant $600 Million Credit to Republic WS2203210694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1815 GMT 22 Mar 94 WS2203210694 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Language: Belarusian Article Type:BFN [Text] The World Bank will grant huge credits to Belarus. [words indistinct] will receive [word indistinct] to $600 million in accordance with a memorandum signed by Belarusian Prime Minister Vyacheslav Kebich and [name indistinct], chairman of the World Bank mission to Belarus. The loans are being issued for 15 years with a delay in the first payment. By the way, the World Bank had already extended two credits to Belarus: Around $17 million for reforming the management bodies, and $120 million -- for importing vital resources and goods.
